                    },
                    "body": "Zend_Rest_Route should support http:\/www.example.com\/{module}\/{controller}\/{idvalue}\r\n\r\nSo is this making a POST request to a \/{idvalue} URL to create a new resource, or append to an existing \/{idvalue} resource?",
